da323750d5ad8638bbed71c94","tid":1359903,"uid":276337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:48:08.000Z","msg":"2019年大增O2O門市　增自取點降成本<br />\n<br />\n而O2O門市對公司來說有更大作用，例如美孚新邨、大圍、大埔等門市，自取訂單數量超越了配送到戶訂單，能直接減低配送成本。<br />\n<br />\n公司表示，2019年底目標要開設約120間O2O門市，進一步成新的訂單自取點及步行距離的配送中心，以進一步減低送貨到戶的成本"},{"pid":"4b8be914691bcf7106ef0e0b530f255c145b7567","tid":1359903,"uid":276337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:58:53.000Z","msg":"有個朋友係入面做送貨..話呢貨多到 日日都送五曬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f853669f6c97a6c72d425794940028bf1d6516","tid":1359903,"uid":248499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"友商士多 出左事之後，全部包派司機都過4萬一個月，派大屋苑 一定過5萬"},{"pid":"1f1af58647bf53ed4b9d4e5f60afd030a5856f08","tid":1359903,"uid":276337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkN8QSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrkN8QSV.png&h=0fa30ae0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"691c609c8f0cfea74788ae5b1957e6acf599ed02","tid":1359903,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b8be914691bcf7106ef0e0b530f255c145b7567","tid":1359903,"uid":276337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:58:53.000Z","msg":"有個朋友係入面做送貨..話呢貨多到 日日都送五曬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:55:31.000Z","msg":"唔夠司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a65d4e63799cef6ddf719dbb8aaafc474a85c71","tid":1359903,"uid":276337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"691c609c8f0cfea74788ae5b1957e6acf599ed02","tid":1359903,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b8be914691bcf7106ef0e0b530f255c145b7567","tid":1359903,"uid":276337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:58:53.000Z","msg